ne content\\n    Close() error                    // Kill session\\n}\\n```\\n\\n**Agent Implementations:**\\n- `claudecode` - Real Claude Code agent via `claude` CLI\\n- `gemini` - Real Gemini CLI agent via `gemini` CLI\\n- `opencode` - Real OpenCode agent via `opencode` CLI\\n- `cursor` - Real Cursor agent via `cursor` CLI\\n- `copilot-cli` - Real Copilot CLI agent via `copilot` CLI\\n- `factoryai-droid` - Factory AI Droid (Gemini variant)\\n- `vogon` - Deterministic fake agent (E2E canary)\\n\\n**Concurrency Control:**\\n- `RegisterGate(name, defaultMax)` - Set max concurrent tests (overridable via `E2E_CONCURRENT_TEST_LIMIT`)\\n- `AcquireSlot(ctx, agent)` - Wait for available slot\\n- `ReleaseSlot(agent)` - Free slot after test\\n\\n---\\n\\n### **10. Key Files Summary**\\n\\n**Agent Interface & Registry:**\\n- `/Users/nodo/work/cli/cmd/entire/cli/agent/agent.go` - Core interfaces\\n- `/Users/nodo/work/cli/cmd/entire/cli/agent/registry.go` - Registration + discovery\\n- `/Users/nodo/work/cli/cmd/entire/cli/agent/types.go` - Type definitions\\n\\n**External Agents:**\\n- `/Users/nodo/work/cli/cmd/entire/cli/agent/external/external.go` - External agent wrapper\\n- `/Users/nodo/work/cli/cmd/entire/cli/agent/external/types.go` - Protocol types\\n- `/Users/nodo/work/cli/cmd/entire/cli/agent/external/discovery.go` - Binary discovery via PATH\\n\\n**Vogon (CLI Agent):**\\n- `/Users/nodo/work/cli/cmd/entire/cli/agent/vogon/vogon.go` - Agent implementation\\n- `/Users/nodo/work/cli/cmd/entire/cli/agent/vogon/hooks.go` - Hook handling\\n\\n**Vogon (Binary):**\\n- `/Users/nodo/work/cli/e2e/vogon/main.go` - Standalone binary (444 lines)\\n\\n**E2E Test Infrastructure:**\\n- `/Users/nodo/work/cli/e2e/README.md` - Documentation\\n- `/Users/nodo/work/cli/e2e/agents/agent.go` - E2E agent interface\\n- `/Users/nodo/work/cli/e2e/agents/vogon.go` - E2E Vogon adapter\\n- `/Users/nodo/work/cli/e2e/agents/tmux.go` - tmux session manager\\n- `/Users/nodo/work/cli/e2e/testutil/repo.go`