ession directory\\n- `resolve-session-file --session-dir <dir> --session-id <id>` - Returns file path\\n- `get-session-id` (stdin: HookInput JSON) - Returns session ID\\n- `read-session` (stdin: HookInput JSON) - Returns `AgentSessionJSON`\\n- `write-session` (stdin: AgentSessionJSON) - Writes session\\n- `format-resume-command --session-id <id>` - Returns resume command\\n\\n*Transcript chunking:*\\n- `chunk-transcript --max-size <bytes>` (stdin: transcript bytes) - Returns `ChunkResponse`\\n- `reassemble-transcript` (stdin: `ChunkResponse` JSON) - Returns reassembled bytes\\n\\n*Hooks (if `capabilities.hooks` true):*\\n- `parse-hook --hook <name>` (stdin: hook JSON) - Returns `agent.Event` JSON or `null`\\n- `install-hooks [--local-dev] [--force]` - Returns `HooksInstalledCountResponse`\\n- `uninstall-hooks` - No output\\n- `are-hooks-installed` - Returns `AreHooksInstalledResponse`\\n\\n*Analysis (if `capabilities.transcript_analyzer` true):*\\n- `get-transcript-position --path <path>` - Returns `TranscriptPositionResponse`\\n- `extract-modified-files --path <path> --offset <n>` - Returns `ExtractFilesResponse`\\n- `extract-prompts --session-ref <ref> --offset <n>` - Returns `ExtractPromptsResponse`\\n- `extract-summary --session-ref <ref>` - Returns `ExtractSummaryResponse`\\n\\n*Optional:*\\n- `prepare-transcript --session-ref <ref>` - Prep before read\\n- `calculate-tokens --offset <n>` (stdin: transcript) - Returns `TokenUsageResponse`\\n- `generate-text --model <model>` (stdin: prompt text) - Returns `GenerateTextResponse`\\n- `write-hook-response --message <msg>` - Write response to user\\n- `extract-all-modified-files --offset <n> --subagents-dir <dir>` (stdin: transcript) - Includes subagents\\n- `calculate-total-tokens --offset <n> --subagents-dir <dir>` (stdin: transcript) - Includes subagents\\n\\n**Wrapping (`external/capabilities.go`):**\\n- `Wrap(externalAgent)` returns agent wrapped as implementing ALL optional interfaces\\n- `wrappedAgent` forward